1
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:31,140
Why are you sitting outside? Where is Su Wan?

2
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,610
Why are you here?

3
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:36,640
To see her.

4
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:38,320
Come on.

5
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:41,009
She doesn't want to see you. Please leave.

6
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,600
Yuding, I'm done with the checkup.

7
00:01:43,600 --> 00:01:44,240
Come in.

8
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:46,160
Hello.

9
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:53,000
Why did you come in? Who let you in?

10
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,160
I am indeed a bit late today.

11
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,930
I'll arrive earlier tomorrow.

12
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,480
Are you upset?

13
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,440
What's your relationship?

14
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:05,000
That you need to come every day?

15
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,460
Why don't you just go home to be with Bai Qing?

16
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,960
Why would I be with her?

17
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,400
You know it yourself.

18
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:20,440
Yaqi came back yesterday and said...

19
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:22,370
The day Gao Chenyang harassed you,

20
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:25,360
a car happened to be parked at the alley entrance

21
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:27,210
and caught it on camera.

22
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,060
He gave me the memory card.

23
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,400
That's wonderful.

24
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:32,400
I got the video,

25
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:35,640
but this involves your personal reputation,

26
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:38,040
so I don't plan to release it.

27
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:40,700
I won't do this just to clear the factory's name.

28
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:41,850
Don't worry.

29
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:49,410
Yaqi will hold another event on Saturday.

30
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:51,240
Will you

31
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,320
come?

32
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:15,140
Do you think Bai Tianyu is thick-headed?

33
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:17,000
Can't he tell that you're angry?

34
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:19,120
If they hadn't brought the evidence

35
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,200
so we don't have to pay,

36
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:22,930
I would definitely beat him up.

37
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:26,700
You're still thinking about beating him up?

38
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,520
He probably

39
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,360
won't come again.

40
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,690
I don't want him to come.

41
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,240
Come on.

42
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,800
Your thoughts are written all over your face,

43
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,460
my hopelessly romantic lady.

44
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,320
Aren't you the same?

45
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,760
I treat you as my best friend,

46
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:45,760
but you want to be my sister-in-law.

47
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:49,020
Me? What nonsense are you talking about?

48
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,100
Here you go.

49
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:33,000
I don't know who left it at the triage desk.

50
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,260
They said it's for you.

51
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:36,320
Thank you.

52
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:45,320
I'm asking if you believe it.

53
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:45,980
Dare to bet?

54
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,640
Let's bet. Who's afraid?

55
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,720
It's a deal.

56
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:52,920
The loser has to be the winner's underling for a month.

57
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,280
Okay.

58
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,770
I bet Su Wan will definitely attend the event.

59
00:06:57,960 --> 00:07:01,000
And they'll definitely get back together.

60
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,200
Impossible.

61
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:06,040
Su Wan saw through Bai Tianyu a long time ago.

62
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,400
A three-legged toad is hard to find.

63
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:09,640
But two-legged men are everywhere.

64
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,800
Just wait to be my underling.

65
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,160
When I win,

66
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,220
I'll let you be my girlfriend.

67
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:30,960
About resigning,

68
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,570
I suggest you think it over carefully.

69
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,880
After all, you're about to be promoted to principal.

70
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:37,480
I've already thought it through.

71
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,340
Over the years,

72
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:40,360
I've basically spent all my time

73
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,560
on teaching.

74
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,640
So I think it's time

75
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:45,080
to spend some quality time with her.

76
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:46,920
Su Wan is exactly like you.

77
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,960
Once she sets her mind on something,

78
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:51,120
no one can change it.

79
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:53,940
She doesn't have my boldness.

80
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:58,210
You really haven't changed at all.

81
00:07:58,280 --> 00:08:01,010
You're exactly the same as when we were in school.

82
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,760
However, I do hope Su Wan

83
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:05,920
can surpass you.

84
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:07,760
I hope so.

85
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:27,440
Hello.

86
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:30,120
Will you come to this event?

87
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:34,799
Su Wan.

88
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:38,140
Su Wan, are you listening?

89
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:39,919
Hello?

90
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,159
All packed up.

91
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:45,680
Let's go home.
